FBIS4-8739 "dreeu074_i_94011" FBIS-EEU-94-074 Daily Report 16 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Events in Gorazde -- 16 April Events in Gorazde -- 16 April Pilot Ejected to Safety AU1604172594 Paris AFP in English 1715 GMT 16 Apr 94 AU1604172594 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Brussels, April 16 (AFP) -- The pilot of the Sea Harrier jump jet shot down over Gorazde in Bosnia-Hercegovina ejected from the airplane and escaped with only "minor scratches," a NATO spokesman said here Saturday. He said the aircraft had been on a non-offensive operation over the mainly-Moslem UN-protected "safe area," currently under Serb attack, when it was shot down.
